## Why This Is Asked
Tests practical PCA use on constrained devices, covering missing-data handling, drift awareness, and latency trade-offs in mobile analytics.

## Key Concepts
- On-device PCA and incremental updates
- Imputation and feature scaling for PCA
- Explained variance and component retention criteria
- Loadings interpretation for actionable alerts
- Memory and latency constraints on mobile

## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudo on-device PCA steps (high level)
function trainPCAOnDevice(dataBatch) {
  const imputed = medianImpute(dataBatch);
  const scaled = scaleToUnit(imputed);
  // Incremental fit to update 6 components
  pca.incrementalFit(scaled, 6);
  return pca.transform(scaled);
}
```

